                    <span>This book is a big disappointment for me. It spends 1 page or less on each shot and offers little insight. Be sure to look at the sample pages (particularly excerpts 2, 3 and 4). That's all you get about pan, tilt, and dolly from the book. May be good for your elementary school kid who tells you, "I wanna make a movie!"</span>
                  
              
